{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b846dd847d","title":"特殊阶层，安息吧！","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9972b7f6d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"b846dd847d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"d6e2c0434f","name":"岑超南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9afb5a2d11","type":"title","text":"特殊阶层，安息吧！","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"1fa2778eea","type":"authors","text":"北京大学岑超南","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"dfafd793d3","type":"subtitle","text":"（岑超南：北京大学物理系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"f8dfeb52ef","type":"subtitle","text":"一、在党团员上层份子中有两类人：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"3ac1cc456e","type":"paragraph","text":"第一类：领导所做全是对的，经典著作的话全是对的(以前联共党史的话也全是对的)，只要不同意领导就是思想有问题或者可能是反党，这种人实际是从未思想过，还自以为对党有利，可怜！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"0e86e048f3","type":"paragraph","text":"第二类：纯粹个人主义者，无非利用职权达到个人卑鄙目的，可耻！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"8836059907","type":"subtitle","text":"二、他们起了什么作用一墙与沟的作用。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"b260f03734","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)向领导主观歪曲报导同学情况：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"27127d16ae","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)维护领导“威信”压制民主。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"34154e7701","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)当领导作出不合理措施时加以帮忙。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"20fa1ed51b","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)后一类人更进行了私人报复。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"47678cc3c3","type":"subtitle","text":"三、怎样产生的：——领导的官僚主义与宗派主义。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"8e4dfba442","type":"paragraph","text":"领导官僚主义不接近群众，不相信群众，可是领导要工作就要有耳目，由于宗派主义，于是就找党团员这些上层份子为耳目，特殊阶层随而产生！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"3d3cad3658","type":"subtitle","text":"四、应该怎么办——领导清除“三害”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"c04af199cc","type":"paragraph","text":"领导深入群众，信任群众，与群众商量工作自然会好，不必特殊阶层代劳了！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"5a5934dcd4","type":"paragraph","text":"特殊阶层，历史使命已告终了，安息吧！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"b656a97a78","type":"paragraph","text":" 物四　岑超南","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"},{"id":"1cb6c04374","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d"}],"page":{"id":"75b5e83ffe","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b846dd847d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}